{"tid":2278771,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Lisa疑被SM新女團aespa抄襲　網民笑：以為四人女團等於BLACKPINK","createTime":"2020-11-09T10:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T10:38:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8e2c5a71f803e764a5dde74f82420fd9fc46bb6f","tid":2278771,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:47:08.000Z","msg":"SM娛樂新女團aespa將於本月17日出道，作為東方神起、Super Junior、少女時代、SHINee和EXO等的師妹團，理應備受大眾期待。可是新女團未出道就被踢爆醜聞多多，包括嫌前輩醜、洩露公司計劃和又煙又酒等。最近aespa又被指疑似抄襲BLACKPINK Lisa，前路似乎非常不明朗。<br />\n<br />\n官方陸續公開aespa 4位成員Karina、Giselle、Winter和Ningning的造型照，每位成員都有對應的虛擬角色，配合團名「&aelig;」中有「雙面」的意思。可是昨天（8日）SM娛樂公開中國成員Ningning的虛擬角色照後，就因角色太似BLACKPINK Lisa而惹來網民熱議。網民對比兩者照片，不論髮色到角色衣着都非常相似，更批評角色與Ningning完全不像。<br />\n<br />\n由於aespa在Red Velvet Irene及EXO燦烈，分別爆出耍大牌和出軌爭議後仍高調出道，因此普遍韓國粉絲都相當不歡迎新女團出道。現在又被質疑有抄襲Lisa之嫌，有網友留言諷刺「aespa是否太不行了？SM（娛樂）以為4人就是BLACKPINK了嗎？」笑言aespa前路將難以猜測。"},{"pid":"401680fb82f1f4c9a211ef5ad5008fd332139adf","tid":2278771,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201109/402508107877453824048795.jpeg/c42foqgBw0Y-hXAS4Inx1z5SBeV7NggG66VnwuulZ8I?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201109%2F402508107877453824048795.jpeg%2Fc42foqgBw0Y-hXAS4Inx1z5SBeV7NggG66VnwuulZ8I%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=26d0821f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201109/402508629434961920269831.jpeg/t3rxMzLxdMDNRcgra6lYhakkqfJPKXma7vgwc-74MHM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201109%2F402508629434961920269831.jpeg%2Ft3rxMzLxdMDNRcgra6lYhakkqfJPKXma7vgwc-74MHM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=94e185ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201109/402508631968452608184360.jpeg/632wYaxO62fHDtYxl07jeWb2wGGP_0xmblO8SG5TvEg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail